      • FFNativePeerInputStream

        protected FFNativePeerInputStream​()
                           throws java.io.IOException,
                                  javax.sound.sampled.UnsupportedAudioFileException
        Subclasses will open a native stream in this constructor. Do not remove the checked exceptions.
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - if we cannot open the stream because of IO issues (e.g. not found).
        javax.sound.sampled.UnsupportedAudioFileException - if we cannot open the stream, because the format is unsupported
